ideas for expansion on the text based adventure game
ideas are numbered througout this document and the document will refer to the
  number as a refernce to the idea

ideas
1. intergrate story better into game 
2. track player in space to not have rooms be repeats when you re-enter them
3. randomize the end room instead of it being the north east corner
4. create a score after every level that compounds for a final score
5. add a little ascii art to make the game more visually interesting

Difficulty and time
1 - easy, as long as possible
2 - medium, a few hours to code and troulbeshoot
3 - easy, quick
4 - easy, quick
5 - easy, as long as possible

